with a schedule for implementation, adequate to assure prompt correction of any air quality problems. Section 175A(d)
requires that the contingency provisions include a requirement that the State will implement all control measures
that were contained in the SIP prior to redesignation as an attainment area. In this action, USEPA is proposing approval
